    <text>
        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Balt<hi rend="sup">o</hi></placeName> <date>31st Mar 1852</date></p>
			<p>My Dr Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Your valued favor of the<lb/> <date>29th</date> inst at hand yesterday was discussed<lb/> at our Dinner Table&#44; when <persName>Mrs C. Frances</persName>&#44;<lb/> and <persName>Andrew</persName> <del>wtre</del> were all gratified<lb/> to learn that you enjoy&#39;d at least<lb/> as good health as when here&#44; all<lb/> beg to reciprocate your good wishes<lb/> for many returns of the approaching<lb/> holidays&#44; hoping that ere another<lb/> <date>Passover</date> shall come round&#44; you will<lb/> be able to introduce them to <persName>Mrs. Leeser</persName>.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">I would &#39;twere in my power<lb/> to give you any specific information<lb/> relative to the probability of a vessel<lb/> sailing hence for <placeName>Kingston</placeName> after <add>Hebrew</add>&#44;<lb/> in a general way those vessels sail<lb/> without advertisement and without notice<lb/> and if you <sic>enquire</sic> of the consignees&#44;<lb/> the general answer is&#44; &#34;she is bound<lb/> for the <placeName>W. Indies</placeName>&#34; I shall try and<lb/> keep on the look out however&#44;</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p>and endeavor to inform you&#44; meanwhile<lb/> however I would advise you by all<lb/> means to write to <persName>Mr. Abm. Lazarus</persName><lb/> at <placeName>New York</placeName> &#40;formerly of <placeName>Kingston</placeName>&#41; who<lb/> would be much more likely to procure<lb/> a passage from <placeName>New York</placeName>&#44; and at<lb/> lower rates too than from here<lb/> besides which he might possibly<lb/> be of service to them otherwise<lb/> having a vast family connexion<lb/> throughout the <placeName>Island</placeName>.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Excuse haste and believe me</p>
          <p rend="indent(4)">Yours most Truly</p>
          <p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">E. P. Cohen</persName></p>
		<pb n="3"/>
			<p><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">mail&#160;&#160;<placeName>Pa</placeName></p>
          
        </body>
